# Demo: epic show — the status-grouped lipgloss/v2 tree. Regenerate with `just gifs`.
Output assets/epic-show.gif
Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 16

Type "tskflwctl epic show 18-tui-bubble-tea-interactive-planning-browser"
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
